  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, whisk together coconut milk, fish sauce, brown sugar, and sliced chili peppers. Add the lamb and marinate for at least 2 hours, or overnight.",
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat. Thread marinated lamb onto skewers.",
    "Brush grill with peanut oil to prevent sticking. Grill lamb skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, make the peanut sauce by blending peanuts, palm sugar, tamarind paste, and lime juice in a blender until smooth.",
